and start practicing.

313
00:14:26,833 --> 00:14:28,666
They try to hide it from you,
but Mom and Dad are starting

314
00:14:28,750 --> 00:14:32,250
to get nervous about
what you're gonna do, Will.

315
00:14:32,333 --> 00:14:33,833
[YOUNG BLACK]
Hmm.

316
00:14:33,916 --> 00:14:36,916
I'm just not sure if I'm
really cut out for it, y'know?

317
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:38,333
[YOUNG WHITE]
What are you talking about?

318
00:14:38,416 --> 00:14:40,291
You're perfect for it!

319
00:14:40,375 --> 00:14:41,791
[WHITE]
Dad!

320
00:14:41,875 --> 00:14:43,083
Mom!

321
00:14:43,166 --> 00:14:44,541
Will!

322
00:14:44,625 --> 00:14:45,916
[heavy breathing]

323
00:14:46,000 --> 00:14:47,291
[explosion]

324
00:14:47,375 --> 00:14:48,916
[coughing]

325
00:14:49,000 --> 00:14:50,541
[YOUNG WHITE] And if you
ever get anxious about

326
00:14:50,625 --> 00:14:51,541
going off on your own,

327
00:14:51,625 --> 00:14:53,250
I'll come with you.

328
00:14:53,333 --> 00:14:54,583
[gasps]

329
00:14:55,875 --> 00:14:57,125
[vomits]

330
00:14:58,416 --> 00:15:00,750
[coughs]

331
